Provides: vencord-desktop
Description: Custom Discord client with Vencord preinstalled
 Vesktop is a custom Discord desktop app that is much more lightweight
 and faster than the official Discord app. It bundles Vencord for
 enhanced customization and features.
 .
 Main features:
  * Vencord preinstalled
  * Linux Screenshare with sound & Wayland support
  * Better privacy — Discord has limited system access
  * Uses system Electron for better integration
 .
 This package repackages the official upstream .deb for Devuan.
